        <article class="post-796 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-uncategorized" id="post-796" role="article">
         <header class="entry-header">
          <h1 class="entry-title">
           <a href="https://bc2.berkeley.edu/2018/06/another-year-another-successful-bc2/" title="Another year, another successful BC2!">
            Another year, another successful BC2!
           </a>
          </h1>
         </header>
         <div class="entry-content">
          <!--START JUICEBOX EMBED-->
          <script type="text/javascript">
           new juicebox({
		backgroundColor: "rgba(34, 34, 34, 1)",
		containerId: "juicebox-container9",
		configUrl: "https://bc2.berkeley.edu/wp-content/plugins/wp-juicebox/config.php?gallery_id=9",
		galleryHeight: "600px",
		galleryWidth: "100%"
	});
          </script>
          <div id="juicebox-container9">
          </div>
          <!--END JUICEBOX EMBED-->
          <p>
           The 7th annual Berkeley Communicators Conference proved to be a jam packed day of talks, panels, knowledge sharing and networking. Campus communicators from all backgrounds came together at International House to learn about subjects ranging from branding and inclusive language to email marketing and productivity tools. Make sure to check out the marketing work from this year’s
           <a href="http://bc2.berkeley.edu/contest/">
            Brand Awards winners
           </a>
           and keep the knowledge sharing going by joining the
           <a href="https://www.facebook.com/groups/calcommcomm/">
            BC2 Facebook group
           </a>
           . See you next year, Berkeley communicators!
          </p>
         </div>
         <!-- .entry-content -->
        </article>
